{"tid":486012,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"魚肉腸，邊隻牌子好?","createTime":"2017-12-01T12:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T13:03:40.000Z","uid":90866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3aea31b2e7b6f153fa52f6948504e9f639d8bacc","tid":486012,"uid":90866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/202653_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F202653_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f5ca1e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從易入手，味道黎講，善子牌真係唔差。<br />\n<br />\n但我多數會為左方便食而買4洲既易撕紅貼包裝，雖然味道真心差d&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n最後係千古難題，係街度，又無剪刀，到底無易撕貼既腸，應該點開先最方便?"},{"pid":"e49ca9c6505c2f282a62c38d9a4b7172234e1d42","tid":486012,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"好多年前食過一隻叫辣味媽媽勁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 善字牌蒜味都唔錯"},{"pid":"de2eb49a47cae60dea42959a31a081a20572cd00","tid":486012,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都係用口咬開個頭然後撕開"},{"pid":"3c22bfddfafac18276a152ef41794e00697ba71c","tid":486012,"uid":41801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:46:25.000Z","msg":"中間對半扭開"},{"pid":"ce45a6b594e8c718d8006853ad36157b7661bcae","tid":486012,"uid":71391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"咬住個扣之後不停扭<br />\n扭到盡佢就會開得好型"},{"pid":"8c44b64a7b554b351910a9d787e8dad66688761a","tid":486012,"uid":90866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中間對半扭開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎個方法，要用力技佢出黎&hellip;&hellip;會變成溶溶爛爛咁，雖然係無工具既情況下最正解既做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3d97014c3924be4333245e960cdb09387be457","tid":486012,"uid":90866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"同埋用口咬個頭，唔會成陣金屬味同整親隻牙?"},{"pid":"cc0708670b0326efd8cffc49d93adef0efd00e26","tid":486012,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋用口咬個頭，唔會成陣金屬味同整親隻牙?</blockquote><br />\n唔會架，唔是咬正個金屬位，係咬佢側邊啲膠，咬開少少就可以撕開，之後就成條腸露出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}